      { text: 'CRM features', url: '/martial-arts-software/' },
      { text: 'See pricing', url: '/pricing/' }
    ]
  },
  {
    question: "How does CRM help convert leads to students?",
    answer: "CRM increases conversions through automated lead response (within 4 minutes vs hours manually), systematic follow-up sequences that prevent leads from falling through cracks, trial class scheduling automation with reminder sequences, lead source tracking to identify best marketing channels, and nurture campaigns for not-yet-ready prospects. Schools using CRM see 42% lead conversion vs 24% without systematic follow-up.",
    links: [
      { text: 'Lead management', url: '/martial-arts-software/' },
      { text: 'Marketing guide', url: '/blog/martial-arts-marketing-tips/' }
    ]
  },
  {
    question: "What's the difference between martial arts CRM and general CRM?",
