    answer: "Automated follow-up sequences trigger based on lead actions and time intervals. When someone inquires, they immediately receive confirmation and school information. Day 2: Follow-up offering trial class. Day 4: Additional value content about benefits. Day 7: Special offer or urgency element. After trial class: Immediate thank-you, next-day enrollment invitation, ongoing nurture if not enrolled. Automation ensures 95% follow-up completion vs 35% manual completion.",
