  {
    question: "Can CRM track lead sources and marketing ROI?",
    answer: "Yes, good martial arts CRM tracks where each lead originated (Google Ads, Facebook, referral, walk-in, event), calculates cost per lead by source, measures conversion rates by channel, identifies which marketing generates highest lifetime value students, and attributes revenue back to original source. This data shows whether your £500/month Facebook ads generate better ROI than £300/month Google Ads based on actual enrollments and lifetime value.",
